OL,3,CRobbery in England and Wales rises
OL,4,Cback to pre pandemic levels
OL,6,FITV News' Mahatir Pasha explains the
OL,7,Flatest crime statistics, which include
OL,8,Fa sharp increase in retail crime and
OL,9,Fviolent offences
OL,11,FRobbery and violence involving injury
OL,12,Fhave risen back up to levels not seen
OL,13,Fsince before the pandemic in England
OL,14,Fand Wales, according to the Office for
OL,15,FNational Statistics (ONS).
OL,17,FThe number of robberies rose to around
OL,18,F139,000 recorded incidents between
OL,19,F2023 and 2024, compared to 60,000 the
OL,20,Fyear before.
