OL,3,CRobbery in England and Wales rises
OL,4,Cback to pre pandemic levels
OL,6,FData from the ONS also found incidents
OL,7,Fof "snatch theft" had doubled between
OL,8,F2023 and 2024 compared to the year
OL,9,Fbetween 2022 and 2023. The number of
OL,10,Fincidents jumped from 32,000 to
OL,11,Fapproximately 78,000.
OL,13,FMore than 469,000 shoplifting offences
OL,14,Fwere recorded between June 2023 and
OL,15,FJune 2024, up from around 365,000
OL,16,Fincidents between June 2022 and June
OL,17,F2023.
