OL,3,CRobbery in England and Wales rises
OL,4,Cback to pre pandemic levels
OL,6,FThe ONS report said this is the
OL,7,Fhighest figure since current police
OL,8,Frecording practices began for the year
OL,9,Fending March 2003.
OL,11,FThe data published on Thursday follows
OL,12,Ffigures from earlier this year, which
OL,13,Fshowed shoplifting was already at its
OL,14,Fhighest level in England Wales since
OL,15,Fpolice records began in 2003.
OL,17,FFigures also show levels of crime
OL,18,Fexperienced by people have generally
OL,19,Fdecreased across the past ten years,
OL,20,Fwith some exceptions, including sexual
OL,21,Fassault.
